These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, lemonade
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage         | sprite | coffee   | lemonade |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike | car        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, pop, gospel
1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the fan of indie##7
2. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | tea | cola   | soy-milk   |
| Music-Genre        | pop | gospel | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, nectarine, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, mouse
1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the owner of the cat##7
3. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | nectarine | strawberry | cauliflower |
| Pet   | cat       | mouse     | rat         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, bartender
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, lavender, chestnut
1. the bartender is not to the right of the architect##8
2. the bartender is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person who likes grey is somewhere between the person who likes lavender and the analyst##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | analyst | bartender | architect |
| Color   | chestnut  | grey | lavender    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, sprite
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
4. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | sprite | almond-milk |
| Pet           | horse    | turtle      | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, security-guard
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, april, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
2. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
3. the security-guard is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
4. the photographer is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | photographer | dancer | security-guard |
| Birthday   | march        | april   | december     |

