.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, scooter
1. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the scooter and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
3. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
4. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | sprite |
| Transport        | scooter      | motorbike    | subway |

