2. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
4. the egyptian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | turkish | dutch    | egyptian |
| Hobby         | singing  | dancing | traveling |

