.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake, lizard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Pet          | lizard | rabbit  | snake |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | drama | romance   |

