.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, house
3 different games are played: poker, whist, chess
1. the fan of house is not to the right of the person playing whist##8
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of house is between the fan of electronic and the fan of d&b##2
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the fan of electronic is not to the left of the person playing whist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | house      | electronic |
| Game         | poker | whist | chess     |

