.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-18::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, roller, scooter
3 different pets are kept: fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is not the person driving the ship##6
2. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Transport   | roller | scooter | ship    |
| Pet    | goat   | fish      | guinea-pig |

