.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-19::.
City: prague, nizza, rome
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, canadian, turkish
1. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
2. the turkish is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to nizza##7
4. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the australian##8
5. the australian is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| City   | prague   | rome    | nizza  |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish | australian |

