.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, video-games
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, snooker
1. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person playing snooker and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
2. the person playing chess is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | board-games | magic-tricks | video-games |
| Game   | snooker  | monopoly    | chess    |

 